Series title:  Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts 2009, NCJ 247018
Data source:  Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts Program (JEE)
Table 19. Supplemental data for 68 large county governments (revised)
Note: Jurisdictions without data did not report for 2009.
a/ Population data are from the Bureau of the Census, July 1, 2010 county population estimates.
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, county-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" FTE excludes utilities and county-operated liquor stores.
